item.description: ߷ This article is about an overseas member of the Commonwealth of Vekllei 1. Overview Making up the far reaches of Vekllei’s broad autonomous islander community, the West Antilles are full and autonomous members of the Atlantic Commonwealth. KT he West Antilles (commonly The Leeward Isles) is the common name of three autonomous islands that make up the West Antilles, situated offshore of northern Venezuela in the Caribbean Sea.
